Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.90,0:00:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.70,0:00:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐才厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.87,0:00:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第五顺位
