Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.80,0:07:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.70,0:07:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都知道建造中的新型机吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.51,0:07:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会要他们提早完成装备组装 参加这次的作战
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.81,0:07:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台Buster Machine已经苏醒了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.88,0:07:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那么简单就能苏醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.55,0:07:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使装备组装完成 有一半还是无法苏醒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.05,0:07:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾听说过它会被销毁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.55,0:07:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.52,0:07:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁来驾驶？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.93,0:07:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让诺诺驾驶新的Buster Machine吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.04,0:07:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感动！太感动了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.31,0:07:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又离诺诺莉莉的梦想更近一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这只笨鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.95,0:07:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶当然是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.95,0:07:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.85,0:07:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下就可以赢拉尔克了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.85,0:07:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了 来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:07:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.82,0:08:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.93,0:08:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这台是隔了数十年才制造的新型机
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.99,0:08:08.96,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Buster Machine·quatre-vingt-dix
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.99,0:08:08.96,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}【quatre-vingt-dix】
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.99,0:08:08.96,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\pos(35,35)}法语数字90
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.87,0:08:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是还没有战斗经验值的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.51,0:08:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶员的选定基准
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.11,0:08:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说会和现有的Buster Machine不同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.31,0:08:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.75,0:08:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fs28}这表示诺诺也有机会是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.85,0:08:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的Buster Machine是否会苏醒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.52,0:08:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟首位驾驶员有很大的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.99,0:08:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且听说操纵技术也很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.89,0:08:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fs28}关于操纵技术
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fs28}我曾被姐姐称赞过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.13,0:08:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fs28\fad(100,200)}哼 哼 自满中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.79,0:08:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思是说还没决定是我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.00,0:08:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的你不能驾驶Buster Machine
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.80,0:08:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是规定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.51,0:08:48.39,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木星 南特拉斯 住宅区
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.44,0:08:50.37,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同区 -271层1b-3
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.41,0:08:52.58,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,民生局医院 木星分院
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.64,0:08:53.46,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙放射线病房大楼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.61,0:08:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.75,0:08:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.29,0:09:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么可能会那么简单就得宇宙放射线病
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.72,0:09:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然说什么没诊断书就不能驾驶Buster Machine
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.19,0:09:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么问题都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.63,0:09:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,quatre-vingt-dix要由我来驾驶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.60,0:09:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这表示我们是竞争对手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.34,0:09:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你什么都没搞懂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.01,0:09:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.49,0:09:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.92,0:09:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得那个人是在这里转弯的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.96,0:09:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能在这种地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.29,0:09:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼吸一点新鲜空气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.13,0:09:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.28,0:10:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么古老的宇宙都市
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.98,0:10:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是第一次来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.55,0:10:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是在人类被关在太阳系之前就已经存在的遗迹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.19,0:10:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里真的比月球的冻京还古老吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.59,0:10:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它本来是为了与宇宙怪兽作战而建造的战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.13,0:10:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如在战场上被击沉或许还比较幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.23,0:10:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其露出这种丑陋的姿态…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.51,0:10:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霉味好重哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.35,0:10:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙船时代的通道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.85,0:10:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来在区域规划时被保留了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.59,0:10:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 果然找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.12,0:10:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是正牌的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.43,0:10:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的秘密基地 有被大人发现过吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.90,0:10:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们一定是Topless
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.56,0:10:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.30,0:10:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还在见习中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.50,0:10:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.70,0:10:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.21,0:11:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些小鬼是哪来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.74,0:11:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然耍别人还偷人家东西 胆子实在有够大…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.01,0:11:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们觉得不这么做的话 你们是不会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.28,0:11:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你真是Topless的话 有件事希望你能帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.68,0:11:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.79,0:11:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让这里下雪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.22,0:11:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让这座没有天空的宇宙都市下雪？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.23,0:11:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.70,0:11:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得到雪对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.44,0:11:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是却降不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.21,0:11:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜是因为太冷而冻住了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.91,0:11:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个白白又亮亮的东西 如果飘了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.88,0:11:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会很好玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.48,0:11:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 让雪飘下来好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.22,0:11:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是星星吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.22,0:11:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.36,0:11:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.06,0:11:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想一起堆雪人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.03,0:11:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.30,0:12:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说嘛 琪可
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.77,0:12:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是小孩子气
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.97,0:12:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Topless的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.94,0:12:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是能让大家幸福吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.88,0:12:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有想过Buster Machine的幸福吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.35,0:12:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.68,0:12:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦醒了过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.92,0:12:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也一定会为人类赴死作战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.22,0:12:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为它被创造的目的就是如此 所以也是理所当然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.16,0:12:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.33,0:12:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当初你身为dix-neuf的驾驶员那时
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.86,0:12:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有想过这种事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.30,0:12:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.13,0:12:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果现在你还能跟它交谈的话 你想问看看吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.90,0:12:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像诺诺这样的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.54,0:12:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能成为quatre-vingt-dix的驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.54,0:12:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对它来说或许就会很幸福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.58,0:12:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这是不可能的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.34,0:12:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼可拉可不这么想哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.05,0:12:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女孩很可能是Topless
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.58,0:12:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是真的这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:12:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于最近一直在下沼气雨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挖掘的进度有点落后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.79,0:13:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木星急行那边没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.96,0:13:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然连新型机都被派出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.13,0:13:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你们安排的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.33,0:13:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.30,0:13:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这个秘密圈可是受到很多人认同的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.14,0:13:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.71,0:13:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦蟹好好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.87,0:13:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的晚餐也别忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.71,0:13:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别搀和了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.18,0:13:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前就先照我们所说的去做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.61,0:13:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个机器人女孩如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.58,0:13:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失的Topless
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.79,0:13:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双胞胎的秘密圈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.06,0:13:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遭到宇宙怪兽袭击的机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.03,0:13:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.43,0:13:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺诺是Topless
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.00,0:13:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺诺可能会被选中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.47,0:13:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Topless的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.47,0:13:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是能让大家幸福吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.71,0:13:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.98,0:13:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们将善用Topless的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.05,0:13:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为全人类…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.52,0:14:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想一起堆雪人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.28,0:14:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堆个雪人好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.29,0:14:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.12,0:14:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能办到的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.84,0:14:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预计木星急行将如同以往
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.44,0:14:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掠过南方住宅区的侧边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.81,0:14:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在各自轨道上的指定地点 发射空间机雷后迅速归航
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.58,0:14:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,48小时后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.42,0:14:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在宇宙怪兽面前布下机雷原
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.12,0:14:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将其诱导至北侧的非住宅区
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自治互助会将在此布下陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.53,0:14:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你很期待诺诺？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.83,0:14:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3、2、1 释放
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个 准备
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.98,0:15:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是说自己的操纵技术很高吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.51,0:15:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琪可
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.31,0:15:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是作战中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.31,0:15:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被责骂的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.41,0:15:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关闭讯号
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.12,0:15:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我一决胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.39,0:15:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.56,0:15:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是早点回去比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.86,0:15:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺诺要回去作战了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.64,0:15:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼可拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.51,0:15:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼可拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.84,0:15:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.28,0:15:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算直接找他谈判吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.12,0:15:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只笨鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.78,0:15:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然罕见地说出“绝不会输给你”这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.42,0:15:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,quatre-vingt-dix是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.36,0:15:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样只会让自己更丢脸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.39,0:15:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然真的生诺诺的气…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.86,0:15:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗唆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法原谅她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.20,0:15:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.57,0:15:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.74,0:16:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们宣誓 将善用Topless的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.04,0:16:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为全人类带来幸福和繁荣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.18,0:16:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要做出无法做到的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.11,0:16:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木星是不可能下雪的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.95,0:16:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Topless真能让人幸福吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.12,0:16:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Topless能治好生病的人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.66,0:16:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Topless能让犯罪消失吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.39,0:16:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能制止战争吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.90,0:16:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Topless能见到死去的人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.50,0:16:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 诺诺才那么努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.17,0:16:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺诺她只是想成为宇宙驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.17,0:16:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后守护大家罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.28,0:16:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁让她是只笨鸟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.33,0:16:59.98,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北特拉斯城壁（坍缩炉心遗址）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.99,0:17:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金星达伶基地的四台机体
