Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.03,0:17:02.88,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}【vingt-deux】
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.03,0:17:02.88,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\pos(35,35)}法语数字22
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.20,0:17:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经封锁了大部分地区
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.42,0:17:05.08,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(425,380)}Buster Machine·soixante
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.42,0:17:05.08,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}【soixante】
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.42,0:17:05.08,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\pos(35,35)}法语数字60
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.58,0:17:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离机雷原还有30
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.50,0:17:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战进入第三阶段
