Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.31,0:17:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认折返点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.74,0:17:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认外围点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.08,0:17:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和果子系迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.74,0:17:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么只来了两架？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.48,0:17:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就说过会这样子了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.85,0:17:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.91,0:17:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先锋部队冲进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.00,0:17:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.94,0:17:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机动防御战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.21,0:17:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,dix-neuf
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.51,0:17:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和果子系的不用出手也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.34,0:17:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要被卷进去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.31,0:17:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终防线交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.98,0:17:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.85,0:17:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法引诱至北侧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.82,0:17:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往南特拉斯去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.42,0:17:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个地区有医院
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.62,0:17:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.63,0:18:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,quatre-vingt-dix无法出动吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.99,0:18:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺诺来驾驶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.23,0:18:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了救那些孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.27,0:18:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在必须用quatre-vingt-dix战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的 它还没苏醒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.17,0:18:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.44,0:18:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,quatre-vingt-dix
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.71,0:18:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快给我醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.98,0:18:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.11,0:18:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来驾驶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琪可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.85,0:18:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你满脑子只想着分数的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.69,0:18:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不回应孩子们的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.22,0:18:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样Buster Machine是不会醒来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.16,0:18:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,500)}Buster
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.53,0:18:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,500)}Beam
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.44,0:18:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,500)}Buster Might
