Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.44,0:18:49.41,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(47,35)}威力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.81,0:18:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,500)\fs22}Burning Wall\N{\fs33}燃烧之墙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想赢拉尔克
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.56,0:19:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她无法在宣誓仪式上说出那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.29,0:19:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么Topless会带给大家幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.23,0:19:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种话…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.07,0:19:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.07,0:19:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像有很厉害的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.24,0:19:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的病我也会帮你治好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.68,0:20:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.98,0:20:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下个月的生日 我们一起来堆雪人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.19,0:20:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.76,0:20:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像不像大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.63,0:20:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑着说“不适合我”的他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.34,0:20:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是宇宙放射线病人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.01,0:20:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明说过要治好他的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.79,0:20:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了谎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.59,0:20:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤了他的心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.66,0:20:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好喜欢他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.83,0:20:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Topless太无力了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.80,0:20:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救不了任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.83,0:20:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连那家医院的孩子也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.50,0:20:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.21,0:21:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.57,0:21:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.78,0:21:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于无法相信自己的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.31,0:21:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Buster Machine是不会借出自己的力量的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.91,0:21:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.15,0:21:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想救那些孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.31,0:21:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.32,0:21:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想被那个人讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.40,0:22:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没完没了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.80,0:22:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方主力突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.47,0:22:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“和果子系”的 麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.10,0:22:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼可拉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.24,0:22:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用Buster X攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.97,0:22:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数量太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.24,0:22:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要进入南特拉斯了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.11,0:22:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有住宅区和医院…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.72,0:22:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,quatre-vingt-dix
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.89,0:22:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁在驾驶？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.77,0:22:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来保护大家
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.54,0:22:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,办得到吧 quatre-vingt-dix
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.97,0:22:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Physical Canceller 全开
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.18,0:22:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exotic Maneuver
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.72,0:22:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耳环也丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.96,0:23:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定不会原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.93,0:23:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是为了那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.30,0:23:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是为了我自己
