Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.27,0:24:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在对我说吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.17,0:25:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跨越了时空…
