Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.65,0:26:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.66,0:26:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.69,0:26:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.83,0:26:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个雪人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.53,0:26:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这般温柔地笑着哦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.11,0:26:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是只笨鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.00,0:28:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土星的卫星泰坦上的遗迹
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.30,0:28:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是外星人的Buster Machine吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.57,0:28:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而当大家在注意这件事时
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.87,0:28:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙怪兽发动了总攻击…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.18,0:28:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 飞跃巅峰2！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.84,0:28:59.50,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复活！！ 传说中的Buster Machine！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.50,0:29:01.14,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬请期待！
